abstract: Stocks rise briskly, led by energy company shares.
lead_paragraph: Reports that OPEC nations had agreed to oil-production cuts sent shares in energy companies, and the price of oil, soaring.
snippet: Reports that OPEC nations had agreed to oil-production cuts sent shares in energy companies, and the price of oil, soaring....

headline.main: Wall St., Powered by Oil, Ends Higher
headline.print_headline: Propelled by Oil, Wall Street Closes Higher
